# Image for Question

## Create image for question


### Resource

`<%= ENV['APP_HOSTNAME'] %>/v1/questions/:question_id/images`


### URL parameters

Parameter | Description | Required
--------- | ----------- | --------
question_id | Question ID | yes


### Query String

Parameter | Description | Required
--------- | ----------- | --------


### HTTP request method

`POST`


### HTTP headers

Key | Value
--------- | -----------
Content-Type | multipart/form-data; boundary=something
access-token | xxxyyyzzz
token-type | Bearer
client | xxxyyyzzz
uid | email


### HTTP body

1. Provide file for multipart form;
1. Attach file to field name: `image[file]`.


### Note


> HTTP example request

```http
POST <%= ENV['DOMAIN_NAME'] %>/v1/questions/1/images
```

```http
